<style>
  .velonna-about {
    background: #0a0a0a;
    color: #f5f0eb;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .about-hero {
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding: 0 5vw 8vw;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.1);
  }
  .about-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0a0a0a 40%, #1a1208 100%);
  }
  .about-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 900px;
  }
  .about-eyebrow {
    font-size: clamp(10px, 1vw, 12px);
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.4);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .about-headline {
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 110px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }
  .about-headline em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.5);
  }
  .about-lead {
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.8vw, 20px);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.7);
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  /* ── STATS STRIP ── */
  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.1);
  }
  .about-stat {
    padding: 4rem 5vw;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.1);
  }
  .about-stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .stat-number {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.4);
  }

  /* ── STORY BODY ── */
  .about-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.1);
  }
  .about-col-left {
    padding: 8vw 5vw;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.1);
  }
  .about-col-right {
    padding: 8vw 5vw;
  }
  .about-section-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.3);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .about-section-heading {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .about-section-text {
    font-size: clamp(14px, 1.4vw, 16px);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.65);
  }
  .about-section-text p { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .about-section-text p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* ── QUOTE BLOCK ── */
  .about-quote-block {
    padding: 8vw 10vw;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.1);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .about-quote-mark {
    font-size: 80px;
    line-height: 0.5;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.1);
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .about-quote-text {
    font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.45;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.9);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .about-quote-attr {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.35);
  }

  /* ── FOUNDER ── */
  .about-founder {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.1);
  }
  .about-founder-image {
    background: #111;
    min-height: 500px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.1);
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .founder-placeholder {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.15);
  }
  .about-founder-text {
    padding: 8vw 5vw;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .founder-name {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .founder-title {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.35);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .founder-bio {
    font-size: clamp(14px, 1.4vw, 16px);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(245,240,235,0.65);
  }
  .founder-bio p { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }

  /* ── CTA STRIP ── */
  .about-cta-strip {
    padding: 6rem 5vw;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .about-cta-heading {
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }
  .about-cta-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .about-cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.3);
    color: #f5f0eb;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .about-cta-btn:hover {
    background: #f5f0eb;
    color: #0a0a0a;
    border-color: #f5f0eb;
  }
  .about-cta-btn.primary {
    background: #f5f0eb;
    color: #0a0a0a;
    border-color: #f5f0eb;
  }
  .about-cta-btn.primary:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: #f5f0eb;
  }

  /* ── MOBILE ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-stat { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.1); }
    .about-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-col-left { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.1); }
    .about-founder { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-founder-image { min-height: 300px; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.1); }
    .about-quote-block { padding: 12vw 6vw; }
    .about-cta-strip { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  }
</style>

<div class="velonna-about">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-content">
      <p class="about-eyebrow">Est. 2024 · Jammu & Kashmir & Indore</p>
      <h1 class="about-headline">
        Tapping<br>
        the <em>silver</em><br>
        luxury gap
      </h1>
      <p class="about-lead">
        International couture aesthetics. Contemporary materials. Accessible price points. Velonna exists because no one else was doing it properly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <div class="about-stats">
    <div class="about-stat">
      <div class="stat-number">₹5.5Cr</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Revenue, first year</div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-stat">
      <div class="stat-number">102</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Years of jewellery heritage</div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-stat">
      <div class="stat-number">18–38</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Age of our customer</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STORY BODY -->
  <div class="about-body">
    <div class="about-col-left">
      <div class="about-section-label">The Gap We Saw</div>
      <h2 class="about-section-heading">Global Couture.<br>Indian Craft.</h2>
      <div class="about-section-text">
        <p>On one side: traditional retail. On the other: high-priced international luxury brands like Bvlgari or Cartier. In the middle, a generation of consumers aged 18 to 38 who want international couture-like designs and globally inspired jewellery — at prices that make sense.</p>
        <p>That is where Velonna was built to live.</p>
        <p>We work with silver, lab-grown stones, and Swarovski crystals — without using cheap materials. The design language is contemporary and luxury-led. We also offer heavy, occasion-wear statement pieces that move between traditional and modern settings.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-col-right">
      <div class="about-section-label">The Heritage</div>
      <h2 class="about-section-heading">102 Years<br>in Retail.</h2>
      <div class="about-section-text">
        <p>Velonna is backed by Khushaal Shyam Narayan Jewellers, a family business with over a century in the jewellery trade — dealing in gold, kundan, polki, diamond jewellery, and traditional Indian and Jammu designs since 1924.</p>
        <p>Velonna was created to tap an entirely new customer base: first nationally, then globally. Built under the Khushaal Shah Amar Nath Jewellers group, it is the contemporary, globally-minded face of that legacy.</p>
        <p>Scaling through a metro-first, franchise-led model — the brand is now expanding city by city across India.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- QUOTE -->
  <div class="about-quote-block">
    <span class="about-quote-mark">&ldquo;</span>
    <p class="about-quote-text">
      There is a large segment of consumers aged 18 to 38 who want two things: international couture-like designs, and jewellery inspired by global brands — both with good materials and accessible price points. That is where Velonna fits in.
    </p>
    <p class="about-quote-attr">Arkit Jain — Founder, Velonna · The Retail Jeweller, March–April 2026</p>
  </div>

  <!-- FOUNDER -->
  <div class="about-founder">
    <div class="about-founder-image">
      <span class="founder-placeholder">Arkit Jain · Founder</span>
    </div>
    <div class="about-founder-text">
      <div class="about-section-label">The Founder</div>
      <div class="founder-name">Arkit<br>Jain</div>
      <div class="founder-title">Founder, Velonna</div>
      <div class="founder-bio">
        <p>Arkit Jain built Velonna to serve a customer the Indian jewellery market was ignoring: young, globally aware, and unwilling to choose between quality and price.</p>
        <p>Growing up in a family with 102 years of jewellery heritage — Khushaal Shyam Narayan Jewellers, dealing in gold, kundan, polki and diamond since 1924 — Arkit saw the same market gap others had overlooked.</p>
        <p>The popularity of duplicate fashion pieces from global houses like Bvlgari or Cartier proved the demand. Velonna was the answer: real materials, contemporary design, global inspiration — built in India.</p>
        <p>In its first year, the brand clocked ₹5.5 crore in revenue. The next phase: metro-first, franchise-led expansion across India.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA STRIP -->
  <div class="about-cta-strip">
    <div class="about-cta-heading">
      Explore<br>the atelier.
    </div>
    <div class="about-cta-links">
      <a href="/collections/silver" class="about-cta-btn primary">Silver</a>
      <a href="/collections/lab-grown-diamonds" class="about-cta-btn">Created Diamonds</a>
      <a href="/pages/contact-us" class="about-cta-btn">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

